Question: Tell me about aman
Answer: Aman Rastogi is an AI/ML Engineer and Software Engineer based in Bengaluru, India. He has experience in building intelligent search systems, RAG pipelines, semantic retrieval, and multi-agent architectures. He is skilled in Python and Java and has worked with technologies such as LangChain, LangGraph, Hugging Face, Vertex AI, and OpenAI to develop scalable LLM-powered applications. Aman has built end-to-end cloud-native systems using Next.js, FastAPI, Supabase, Redis, and Pinecone, collaborating with cross-functional teams to deliver AI-driven solutions for various applications, including enterprise knowledge management, recruitment automation, and financial analytics. He is passionate about applying AI and advanced analytics to transform enterprise workflows.
